title: Person of Interest S4E21 Elias vs Dominic
author: ReWatch TV
comment: Dominic was smart, but Elias was far craftier and more experienced.  In the end, no matter how often Dominic thought he had the upper hand, Elias ALWAYS had another trick up his sleeve.
I laughed when Elias said "You're gonna need a new right hand man"
Elias: "Good news, you have no rat in your organization; bad news, you need a new right hand man".
I love how Elias foreshadowed the death of Link. Asking Dominic if he really wants to know how it feels to be responsible for your friends death...
